#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.1:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Ānisaṃsavagga "
msgstr "1. Benefits "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Kimatthiyasutta "
msgstr "1. What’s the Purpose? "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.1, sc1
msgctxt "an10.1:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an10.1:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "an10.1:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.1:2.1"
msgid "“Kimatthiyāni, bhante, kusalāni sīlāni kimānisaṃsānī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the purpose and benefit of skillful ethics?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:2.2"
msgid "“Avippaṭisāratthāni kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsānī”ti. "
msgstr "“Ānanda, having no regrets is the purpose and benefit of skillful ethics.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.1:3.1"
msgid "“Avippaṭisāro pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of having no regrets?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso”ti → pāmujjattho pāmujjānisaṃsoti (si, pts1) | pāmujjattho pāmujjānisaṃso (s1-3)
msgctxt "an10.1:3.2"
msgid "“Avippaṭisāro kho, ānanda, pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso”ti. "
msgstr "“Joy is the purpose and benefit of having no regrets.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.1:4.1"
msgid "“Pāmojjaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsan”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of joy?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:4.2"
msgid "“Pāmojjaṃ kho, ānanda, pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsan”ti. "
msgstr "“Rapture …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an10.1:5.1"
msgid "“Pīti pana, bhante, kimatthiyā kimānisaṃsā”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of rapture?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:5.2"
msgid "“Pīti kho, ānanda, passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā”ti. "
msgstr "“Tranquility …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.1:6.1"
msgid "“Passaddhi pana, bhante, kimatthiyā kimānisaṃsā”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of tranquility?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:6.2"
msgid "“Passaddhi kho, ānanda, sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā”ti. "
msgstr "“Bliss …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.2, sc7
msgctxt "an10.1:7.1"
msgid "“Sukhaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsan”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of bliss?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:7.2"
msgid "“Sukhaṃ kho, ānanda, samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsan”ti. "
msgstr "“Immersion …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.1:8.1"
msgid "“Samādhi pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of immersion?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:8.2"
msgid "“Samādhi kho, ānanda, yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso”ti. "
msgstr "“Truly knowing and seeing …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an10.1:9.1"
msgid "“Yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsan”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of truly knowing and seeing?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.1:9.2"
msgid "“Yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ kho, ānanda, nibbidāvirāgatthaṃ nibbidāvirāgānisaṃsan”ti. "
msgstr "“Disillusionment and dispassion …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.1:10.1"
msgid "“Nibbidāvirāgo pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso”ti? "
msgstr "“But what’s the purpose and benefit of disillusionment and dispassion?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso → … nisaṃsoti (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an10.1:10.2"
msgid "“Nibbidāvirāgo kho, ānanda, vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso. "
msgstr "“Knowledge and vision of freedom is the purpose and benefit of disillusionment and dispassion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an10.1:11.1"
msgid "Iti kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni avippaṭisāratthāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsāni; "
msgstr "So, Ānanda, the purpose and benefit of skillful ethics is not having regrets. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.2"
msgid "avippaṭisāro pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso; "
msgstr "Joy is the purpose and benefit of not having regrets. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.3"
msgid "pāmojjaṃ pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsaṃ; "
msgstr "Rapture is the purpose and benefit of joy. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.4"
msgid "pīti passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā; "
msgstr "Tranquility is the purpose and benefit of rapture. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.5"
msgid "passaddhi sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā; "
msgstr "Bliss is the purpose and benefit of tranquility. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.6"
msgid "sukhaṃ samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsaṃ; "
msgstr "Immersion is the purpose and benefit of bliss. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.7"
msgid "samādhi yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso; "
msgstr "Truly knowing and seeing is the purpose and benefit of immersion. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.8"
msgid "yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ nibbidāvirāgatthaṃ nibbidāvirāgānisaṃsaṃ; "
msgstr "Disillusionment and dispassion is the purpose and benefit of truly knowing and seeing. "

msgctxt "an10.1:11.9"
msgid "nibbidāvirāgo vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso. "
msgstr "Knowledge and vision of freedom is the purpose and benefit of disillusionment and dispassion. "

#. VAR: aggāya parentī”ti → arahattāya pūrentīti (s1-3)
msgctxt "an10.1:11.10"
msgid "Iti kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni anupubbena aggāya parentī”ti. "
msgstr "So, Ānanda, skillful ethics progressively lead up to the highest.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.1:11.11"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

